.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-OPEN-CONFIRM" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-open-confirm \- show confirmation status of a channel open
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-open-confirm
.I channel_id
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns the current confirmation count vs required confirmations for a
pending channel open.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"channel_id":..., "state":..., "confirmations":N, "confirmations_required":N}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-channel-pending (1),
.BR lightning-channel-info (1)
